Assumed [[Cameo]] device. This device is using [http://www.mediatek.com/en/News/news_content.php?sn=1057 RT6856]. The Ralink chip used for the on-board :wireless again appears to be RT5592 (RTL5592EPL?). *[http://certifications.wi-fi.org/pdf_certificate.php?cid=WFA14995 Wi-Fi Certified] The default SSID formats for the device are '''dlink-XXXX''' (2.4GHz) and '''dlink-media-XXXX''' (5GHz), where :'''XXXX''' appears to be the last two bytes (upper case letters) of the respective interface's MAC address. ==Images== ---- __NOTOC__
